                            to provide a credit link to us. If you have any question, feel free to
                            <a href="http://www.facebook.com/templatemo" target="_parent">contact us</a>. <br><br>
                            Nam nec tellus a odio tincidunt auctor a ornare odio. Sed non mauris vitae erat consequat
                            auctor eu in elit. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per
                            inceptos himenaeos. Mauris in erat justo. Nullam ac urna eu felis dapibus condimentum.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-offset-2">
                          <div class="slider-social">
                            <a href="#" class="tm-social-icon"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="tm-social-icon"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="tm-social-icon"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="tm-social-icon"><i class="fa fa-google-plus"></i></a>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-offset-12">
                          <a href="#" class="tm-home-box-2-link"><i class="fa editTravel fa-edit tm-home-box-2-icon border-left"></i></a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
